# Cloud And CI/CD Governance

- Never hardcode secrets; use managed secret stores.
- Enforce build, test, security scan, and artifact traceability in pipelines.
- Apply environment-specific configuration through controlled promotion.
- Require rollback strategy and health checks for production releases.
- Tag cloud resources consistently by service, owner, and environment.
